{"tid":783574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無人覺得最體現到七夕精神就係扑野","createTime":"2018-08-17T15:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T08:59:08.000Z","uid":22440,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c42bcae01b40d15c471deddb3edf6332efd8ccba","tid":783574,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"試諗下牛郎同織女一年有364 日無得見<br />\n係現代人角度即係long distance la<br />\n有唐代劉言史《七夕歌》：碧空露重新盤濕，花上乞得蜘蛛絲<br />\n借描景 描繪七夕牛郎織女忍左成年火 扑野的意景<br />\n試諗下 成年無見 織女條裙濕曬咁飛落黎條橋到搵牛郎 最後搞到周圍都有蜘蛛絲......<br />\n<br />\n但係呢個節日咁多年黎比人夾硬講成佢地兩個見面 拖手 對望 傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬啊 仔都生左兩件 作呢個故仔果條友自己有無笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後發展到仲好笑 變左做係呢一日求織女保佑自己有一對巧手 好恩緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢地知唔知道牛生同織小姐本身段恩緣差到仆街嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到今時今日班情侶post 相話男友又帶我去邊到邊到食野 送左乜乜乜比我慶祝七夕<br />\n覺得七夕好有意思乜乜物物 真係好想笑<br />\n<br />\n想慶祝七夕 正正經經扑野仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 無乜讀過書 今晚係屋企過"},{"pid":"f4d9b758b265d9dd0fca892ba2fb5c0f2084a7f7","tid":783574,"uid":156821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"哪有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de97265f5c586f869f07b02f062e486ce7b0c4ac","tid":783574,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4d9b758b265d9dd0fca892ba2fb5c0f2084a7f7","tid":783574,"uid":156821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"哪有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba2f91eca246c87b78d366721967d1a8d588790","tid":783574,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"咸濕囝=="}]}